Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維塔的所在?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我像是知道的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說身為變革者的你也不知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我知道在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們打算對維塔做什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維塔原本可是為了我們使用才造出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們打算用維塔做什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞制定這個計劃的真意是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了即將到來的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將到來的對話?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不懂你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是人類的界限啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得自己是萬能的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明這樣被抓起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我這麼說呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 菲露特?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡特納小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐她怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍打了拉塞 還把米蕾娜劫為人質…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡特納她自稱變革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革者!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐她!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有什麼三長兩短
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人質的性命就不能保障了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同類的我和艾紐 思維是可以聯系的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是了解的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦量子波…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐 之後按計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦內系統…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:01:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡…裡特納小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們停手吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話 大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你再往前去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮瑞斯小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為只有你自己才能使用腦量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦內系統被病毒感染了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵分兩路 搜尋米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐到艦橋去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 艾紐在哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮瑞斯小姐你能來真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都把你給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C級腦量子波使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殘次品超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬惡之源就是你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐的仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞艾 斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算拋棄我 一走了之嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以見證世界的變革哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right 我答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為禮物 我把Cherudim也帶上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間多謝你們照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…知道了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真開槍啊… 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人質被奪回了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為被做成女性才會被感情所左右…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐用小型艇逃脫麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這系統怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設定太隨意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三閘門 自己打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後部閘門也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓Cherudim和00去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去向裡本斯解釋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 很抱歉 要以奪回0 Raiser優先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用TRANS-AM了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算損壞這台機體嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們擁有優秀的戰術預報士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 這家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser DOCKING-MODE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統控制權交給00了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制不能!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如洛克昂所說 離萬能還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能放棄0 Raiser了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 還是希望能送上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一份禮物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser的出力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要向我射擊麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來 艾紐!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐·裡特納
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快射擊啊…快給我射啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了什麼待在這裡的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才進入KATARON 成為天行者的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個不中用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾·狄蘭迪!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的覺悟只有這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼點…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾·狄蘭迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的愛你的 萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你不太舒服 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子要配置新藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾馬克 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你可以抑制侵蝕你身體細胞異常的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你要求的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現沒有紛爭的世界統一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了向Gundam報雙親的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…dam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很看好你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台Regnant也是為了你才帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你成為人類最初的變革者 引導這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以麼 露易絲·哈勒維
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 阿爾馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 艦內系統狀況如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航行 戰斗系統都受到了相當大的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始進行殺毒工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但完全被刪除的數據量達到3456
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎也有被變革者帶走的數據資料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統重建所需的時間呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最短需要2210
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡特納小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:10:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在集中精力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩 0 Riser的修理狀況如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛席零件一個一個都換過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 Riser系統的調整要花時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一時半會兒 00可沒法出擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐… 為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為什麼啊 可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會上戰場的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得他們會放過這次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說該做的事情我也會做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是扣下扳機…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不得已的時候我會來做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後那時候只要恨我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在那裡裝帥了 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話 沒有和她戰斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的吧!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能戰斗的理由更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去進行Seravee的出擊准備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡由我來做就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你不是要操作母艦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你會不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 請用Gundam來守衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E傳感器有反應 從速度來看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預測是敵方部隊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦艇的系統已經排不上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00也已經掛彩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的Gundam的話小菜一碟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希林格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等的目的是00的虜獲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也得讓那孩子幫幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡趣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勒維准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新制造的Regnant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是初次上陣 但是期待著你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam上場了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3架…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人數量不多 但是有MA在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前的類型不同麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子束竟然!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然拐彎了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這種威力是…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種攻擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要中招了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想得手!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪裡 艾紐!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機接近 敵機接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼興奮 萊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是好男人別就這麼可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是艾紐!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戲劇性的再會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深愛的女人其實是變革者 是自己的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是 賭上性命的愛情呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐引走了1架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是這邊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃… 這光束!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打開突破口!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HYPERBURST-MODE!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高濃度壓縮粒子 發射!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎… 怎麼會!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HYPERBURST竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios 損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim 正在離開戰斗宙域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00還沒好麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要點時間!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 獠牙!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHIELDBIT ASSAULT-MODE!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們非得戰斗!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為你是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是變革者啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們相互理解了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在虛偽的世界裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說那全都是假的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的思念也是麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情也是麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要上了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干 干什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用問麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次把你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成我的女人!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許你說不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊… 萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的東西就要搶到手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是變革者也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下了哦 00!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來吧 艾紐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革者將領導人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是更加進化的 絕對存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人類看作是平等的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可無法忍受啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量的差距 就讓你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 艾紐!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這… 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得自己是變革者其實真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為… 為什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會遇到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會在這個世界的某個地方擦肩而過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不也好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就可以活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有你在的話就沒什麼活下去的動力了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我們 相互理解了對方對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當然了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋… 你這混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋把艾紐!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙本想要回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是作為變革者 而是作為人類
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.30,0:23:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我們的身邊!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你這混蛋的錯才!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…艾紐……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明心意相通…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天我也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和露易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音在回響…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的聲音在…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.59,0:23:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的… 歌聲……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.99,0:24:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生道路被改變之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.39,0:24:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去血肉之親之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.68,0:24:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏈鎖的憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有用奪去生命來救贖麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 革新之門
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.69,0:24:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 走向門的另一側…
